.TH oma-depends 1  "depends " 
.SH NAME
depends \- List dependencies for the specified package(s)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdepends\fR [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIPACKAGES\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
List dependencies for the specified package(s)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH ARGUMENT
.TP
<\fIPACKAGES\fR>
Package(s) to query dependency(ies) for
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Set output format to JSON
